{
  "_comment": "Data-driven genre root families. infer_root() scans an album's whole tag set and returns the root of the FIRST rule (top to bottom = priority) whose keyword is a substring of any tag. Tags matching no rule fall back to the album's most specific tag (never 'Unknown'). Extend freely.",
